#: ../../Instance_Setup/Instance_Setup.rst:107
#: cfb0db3d5e23418d9c93ddb2d34548d4
msgid ""
"The script writes a file named ``setup.json`` in the same directory. Its "
"structure is:"
msgstr ""
"Скрипт записывает файл с именем ``setup.json`` в тот же каталог. Его "
"структура:"

#: ../../Instance_Setup/Instance_Setup.rst:131
#: 0a2b6c0e312a49de8ed7838e045b3b66
msgid ""
"**Each list contains at most one object.** When a new server or client "
"configuration is added, the entire list for that type is replaced."
msgstr ""
